Title: Up the Volcano
Description:
A whole bunch of our people headed up to the top of the volcano to mount a counter-offensive. There's something horrible brewing up there on the Lost Peak.

They're waiting for you before they make any moves against the pygmies. Those evil little things turned a lot of us into zombies!

$n, save us!
ObjectivesText: Speak with Coach Crosscheck at the Lost Peak on the Lost Isles.
